==Character==
===Appearance===
*Arare has black or gray hair which sweeps off to the side. She wears a smokestack-shaped hat, a short-sleeved white shirt, arm warmers, a skirt with suspenders and black kneehighs. She carries a twin-gun turret and a quadruple torpedo launcher.

==Notes==
*Arare Kai Ni is capable of equipping all kinds of [[List of Landing Crafts by stats|landing crafts]].
*Arare Kai Ni has the sixth highest ASW of all destroyers.

==Trivia==
*Sunk in combat, July 4, 1942.
**She was the first ship of the Asashio Class to be sunk.
**Wreck discovered in June 2007 by expedition searching for submarine ''USS Grunion''.
*Her name means "hail", especially referring to small hailstones.
**It was first carried by the seventh and last Torpedo Boat Destroyer of the Harusame class in 1903.
*Her verbal tic "'ncha" is a reference catchphrase from a character in ''Dr. Slump'', Arale Norimaki (name romanized as Norimaki '''Arare''') 

